---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - OptyP" description="Privacy Policy for OptyP - Professional resume and profile optimization services.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        At OptyP, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. 
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our services.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Personal identification information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and other contact details</li>
            <li><strong>Profile details:</strong> Resume content, LinkedIn profile information, career history, and skills provided for optimization</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Analytics data via cookies and similar technologies to improve our services</li>
            <li><strong>Communication records:</strong> Emails, chat messages, and feedback you provide to us</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <p>Your information is used solely to provide and improve our services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Deliver resume optimization and LinkedIn profile enhancement services</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your projects and provide customer support</li>
            <li>Process payments and send invoices</li>
            <li>Improve our services based on usage analytics</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations and protect against fraud</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-200 mt-4">
            <p class="text-green-800 font-medium">
              âœ“ We never sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes without your explicit consent.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your data from 
            unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Encrypted data transmission (SSL/TLS)</li>
            <li>Secure data storage with access controls</li>
            <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
            <li>Limited access to personal data on a need-to-know basis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p>
            We retain your personal information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this 
            Privacy Policy, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request access to your personal data</li>
            <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request transfer of your data to another service provider</li>
            <li><strong>Withdrawal of consent:</strong> Withdraw consent for data processing at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@optyp.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience and analyze site usage. 
            You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. 
            We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on our website.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions About Our Privacy Policy?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
          For any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please don't hesitate to reach out.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Contact Form:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">Visit our contact page</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>